          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κλαίω</span></b> , ipf. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κλαῖον</span>, iter. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κλαίεσκε</span>, fut. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κλαύσομαι</span>,
          aor. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κλαῦσε</span>: <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">weep, cry;</span>
